Subject: Server Disk Space
Description: Hello, our Netwrix Enterprise Auditor server disk is almost full. I thought all scans data went to the database and wasn't kept on the server localy. Is that normal? Our server disk is 430gb, and currently, FSAA scans occupy 400gb.
What_We_Know__c: The T2 database lives on the local server
Solution_Comment__c:
The customer was low on space, so I advised him to add disk space to his Drive.
I explained to the customer that the T2 database lives on the local server.
